{"tid":1646262,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國皇家海軍教大家乜嘢係「be water」","createTime":"2019-10-11T08:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:23:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7e24207fbb188a81dfb4baf6ef9030941095849d","tid":1646262,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得 &quot;be water&quot; = 轉身逃跑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;be water&quot;喺講緊 Target A有重防, 就轉去無防既Target B, 如此類推...<br />\n成千個 potential targets防都防唔到呀！<br />\n<br />\n班友見到 Target A有重防, 就轉身逃跑, 大叫 &quot;be water&quot;<br />\n嘩屌！乜撚嘢呀家吓？<br />\n<br />\n睇下乜嘢叫軍事戰術：<br />\n<br />\n「1840年6月，懿律率領英國軍艦16艘、武裝輪船4艘、運輸艦28艦、陸軍4,000人，抵達廣州海面，第一次鴉片戰爭正式開始。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">英軍主力抵達廣東後，見廣州一帶布防嚴密</span></strong>，認為在當地採取軍事行動的效果不大，在距離京師較近的地方進行一次有效的打擊，能更有效的逼迫清廷屈服。鑑於此，英方除留四艘軍艦和一艘武裝輪船繼續封鎖珠江口外。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主力艦隊則按照英方既定的對華作戰部署，從廣東啟程北上進攻浙江舟山列島。」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://b.share.photo.xuite.net/ll717592/1b5373e/10917782/508724648_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fb.share.photo.xuite.net%2Fll717592%2F1b5373e%2F10917782%2F508724648_m.jpg&h=36190ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係因為英國皇家海軍be water咁打, 香港先至會被永久割讓 + 開埠！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n屌！1840年既英軍都醒過大多數人！<br />\n<br />\n你班友細個有無讀書架？"},{"pid":"727565ed2c741b06b288b02cd9196d634dfbe494","tid":1646262,"uid":183091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T08:29:30.000Z","msg":"遠水 希望有4000和理非幫手<br />\n<br />\n大家今晚睇左片未呀<br />\n<br />\n除左睇片仲可以宣傳下我地<br />\n<br />\n連登post<br />\n<a href=\"Https://lih.kg/1638741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Https://lih.kg/1638741</a><br />\n<br />\nTg channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youtubefundus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyoutubefundus&d=6p%2BW5